8dff60cc-490f-407b-ba9b-996149e2b4b3	24b10047-e115-45a5-847b-2ebc7ffef6d7	7de19cb6-ad0e-0a27-b290-9bd52b248847	Investors in eco credits often include environmentally-focused funds, green banks, and socially responsible investment firms looking to support sustainability initiatives. Additionally, local governments and community foundations might invest as part of resilience-building efforts. Presenting the tangible benefits of your projects—like improved air quality, reduced flooding risks, and enhanced community spaces—can make these credits more attractive to potential investors who value both ecological impact and community upliftment. Would you like suggestions on how to reach out to these types of investors?	{"text": "Investors in eco credits often include environmentally-focused funds, green banks, and socially responsible investment firms looking to support sustainability initiatives. Additionally, local governments and community foundations might invest as part of resilience-building efforts. Presenting the tangible benefits of your projects—like improved air quality, reduced flooding risks, and enhanced community spaces—can make these credits more attractive to potential investors who value both ecological impact and community upliftment. Would you like suggestions on how to reach out to these types of investors?", "actions": ["REPLY"], "thought": "The user is inquiring about potential investors for eco credits in Red Hook. I'll provide insights on typical investors interested in such projects and how these investments can be framed to attract them."}	a380e976-dc22-416f-b51e-dc7aa63c80a3	agent_response	\N	{"isDm": true, "agent_id": "7de19cb6-ad0e-0a27-b290-9bd52b248847", "agentName": "Narrator", "channelType": "DM"}	2025-08-08 17:20:18.179	2025-08-08 17:20:18.179
