ly with <response> and end with </response>.\\n</output>", "modelKey": "TEXT_LARGE", "provider": "openai", "response": "<response>\\n    <thought>The user is working on an emergency plan for the Red Hook community. I'll provide narrative support by highlighting the importance of resilience and regeneration in emergency planning.</thought>\\n    <actions>REPLY</actions>\\n    <providers></providers>\\n    <text>Creating an emergency plan for Red Hook is a proactive and vital step towards resilience. 🌍 In crafting this plan, consider weaving in elements of regenerative design—such as incorporating green spaces that can manage floodwaters or using local plants to stabilize soil. These actions not only prepare the community for emergencies but also enhance long-term ecological health and community well-being. What specific areas are you focusing on in your plan? I'd be delighted to help explore how regenerative principles can play a role!</text>\\n</response>", "modelType": "TEXT_LARGE", "timestamp": 1754670917179, "executionTime": 6918.589438997209}	useModel:TEXT_LARGE	7de19cb6-ad0e-0a27-b290-9bd52b248847
