fcc6773d-4cce-05d7-9b45-7401cffd2609	messages	2025-08-08 16:33:27.649	{"text": "i want to work on regenerative projeocts in Red Hook, Brooklyn", "source": "client_chat"}	b2ee613b-1415-0d82-b518-b36a24ca1033	7de19cb6-ad0e-0a27-b290-9bd52b248847	66943e9a-82b5-0358-831e-df6453bd72ec	f1315eea-1283-09c7-a171-fd391858e3ca	t	{"raw": {"roomId": "24b10047-e115-45a5-847b-2ebc7ffef6d7", "source": "client_chat", "message": "i want to work on regenerative projeocts in Red Hook, Brooklyn", "metadata": {"isDm": true, "channelType": "DM", "targetUserId": "7de19cb6-ad0e-0a27-b290-9bd52b248847"}, "senderId": "23a12471-8ddf-4f5c-9c5c-1c2ebce5c7f2", "serverId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000", "channelId": "24b10047-e115-45a5-847b-2ebc7ffef6d7", "messageId": "2519fa1d-a8b3-44de-91aa-69180d66da47", "senderName": "User-23a12471"}, "type": "message", "source": "client_chat", "sourceId": "40b0d1b7-5812-4ca2-a71c-dfa176f0cd90"}
fd6886bb-5969-4c86-a940-79e36e921493	messages	2025-08-08 16:33:37	{"text": "That's wonderful to hear! Red Hook, Brooklyn is a community with great potential for regeneration. 🌱 Imagine transforming vacant lots into lush community gardens that not only provide food but also serve as gathering spaces for neighbors. Picture rooftops covered in green infrastructure, capturing rainwater and reducing urban heat. You could be part of initiatives that bring back native plants, inviting pollinators like bees and butterflies back into the cityscape. What specific aspects of regenerative projects are you interested in exploring? Let's craft your unique story within this transformation!", "simple": true, "actions": ["REPLY"], "thought": "The user wants to engage in regenerative projects in Red Hook, Brooklyn. I'll craft a narrative to inspire and guide them on how they can contribute to regenerative efforts there.", "inReplyTo": "16fa438e-f2f8-028b-9475-e94850c3cc78", "providers": []}	7de19cb6-ad0e-0a27-b290-9bd52b248847	7de19cb6-ad0e-0a27-b290-9bd52b248847	66943e9a-82b5-0358-831e-df6453bd72ec	f1315eea-1283-09c7-a171-fd391858e3ca	t	{}
